    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Defensive Awareness — Blocking Triple-Triples</h2>

    <p>Equally important as playing triple-triples is preventing your opponent from landing them. Watch for these warning signs:</p>

    <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
